    "description": "1. Dynamic included components are: Atmosphere (with an embedded soil component), Ocean (with embedded Sea Ice & Ocean Biogeochemistry components) , Land Surface & Subsurface Vegetation, Land Ice for Greenland. An emulator for simulating the Antarctic freshwater flux (on the ocean grid) and a simple yet fast atmosphere CO2 box model  (one global grid point) that replaces the CO2-only version of the TM5 model as a CO2 tracer transport model for closing the carbon cycle. 2. The Atmospheric Chemistry and Aerosols are prescribed. 3. The Antarctic Ice sheet is not modeled itself.",
